Event staff scan registrations and log attendance metrics, distributing tote bags filled with branded notebooks, pens, water bottles, and phone chargers. Inside, attendees engage with kiosks to upload resumes and analyze recruiters, while a robotics startup captivates attention with a small drone flying above its booth. An alumni panel discusses technical interview preparation, and workshops on networking etiquette take place in an adjoining classroom. Throughout the day, students exit with business cards, reminded by recruiters to follow up with personalized emails, as post-event survey links are displayed on monitors near the exit.

A startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session, while consulting and finance firms offer glossy case study booklets, and a cybersecurity company conducts a password cracking challenge on a laptop. Groups of friends mark target employers on the event map, and international students, along with others, queue for advice on visa sponsorship requirements outside the gym, as event staff manage registrations and hand out lanyards. Inside, workshops on networking etiquette and an alumni panel on technical interviews take place in an adjoining classroom. Recruiters distribute tote bags filled with notebooks, and students quietly rehearse elevator pitches against the wall amid the aroma of coffee and catered snacks, while volunteers gather leftover brochures as camera crews capture interviews.
